Allow 32 bit linux to fail late, rather than early (#7434)

32 bit linux buidls fo surge mainline fail so we fatal error
them early. Some folks want to do builds as a submoudle
so make it fail late as an option, which is off by default.

Addresses https://github.com/surge-synthesizer/surge-rack/issues/975